org.gvsig.dwg.lib.readers

Class DwgFileV12Reader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.dwg.lib.readers.DwgFileV12Reader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDwgFileReader

    public class DwgFileV12Reader
extends Object
implements IDwgFileReader
    Reads version 12 dwg files. DWG 13 and DWG 12 are very different formats (nor do DWG 13-14 and 2000). Thats the reason why this IDwgFileReader is very different from the rest. Documentation of reverse engineering of the format: http://www.iwriteiam.nl/DWG12.html
